These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
House: victorian, art-deco, tower, farmhouse
There 4 different types of food: orange, zucchini, pomegranate, peach
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, german, dutch, russian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, baccarat, davidoff, vegafina
1. the person eating zucchini is the victorian house##1
2. the russian is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
3. the dutch is the person eating orange##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the art-deco house##1
6. the chinese is on the left of the german##1
7. the person eating zucchini is the aristoff-smoker##1
8. the german is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
9. the farmhouse house is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| House         | victorian  | farmhouse  | art-deco | tower |
| Food           | zucchini | orange | peach  | pomegranate  |
| Nationality   | russian       | dutch      | chinese | german      |
| Cigar           | aristoff          | baccarat     | davidoff    | vegafina     |

