.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, cat, goat, horse
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, aquamarine, turquise, ebony
There are 4 different nationalities: british, thai, chinese, french
The people have 4 different jobs:  firefighter, writer, horsecher, analyst
1. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
2. the french is the firefighter##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
4. the horsecher is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
5. the french is on the left of the british##1
6. the owner of the goat is the chinese##1
7. the thai is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
8. the horsecher is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
9. the firefighter is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Pet      | goat     | rat       | cat | horse        |
| Color          | ebony     | aquamarine       | turquise   | ivory   |
| Nationality   | chinese      | thai       | french     | british    |
| Job         | horsecher | analyst | firefighter | writer |

