.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
City: liverpool, marseilles, edinburgh, nizza
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold, sunflower, amaryllis
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, snowmobile, van, train
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, may, december
 1. the person traveling to nizza is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the far right##1
 3. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| City      | marseilles | liverpool       | nizza        | edinburgh        |
| Flower           | marigold   | sunflower | begonia   | amaryllis |
| Transport   | ship     | snowmobile    | train | van        |
| Birthday           | may         | march  | december       | february         |

