.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, tomato, eggplant, kale
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, lemonade, coffee
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, yellow, white, black
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, havana, montecristo, aristoff
1. the person who likes white is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
4. the person eating kale is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person eating kale is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
8. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1
9. the montecristo-smoker is the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food           | tomato   | pomegranate  | kale | eggplant |
| Beverage   | lemonade | coffee       | water       | 7up     |
| Color   | white       | black    | yellow     | orange  |
| Cigar           | havana     | montecristo | aristoff     | vegafina         |

