.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, mirinda, fanta
There 4 different types of food: carrot, lettuce, lemon, raspberry
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, siglo, cain, vegafina
House: art-deco, tower, modern, cape-cod
1. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
2. the art-deco house is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the tower house is on the far left##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
6. the cape-cod house is the cain-smoker##1
7. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
9. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage           | tea  | mirinda    | coffee | fanta |
| Food   | lemon      | lettuce    | carrot         | raspberry    |
| Cigar   | siglo   | bongani     | cain          | vegafina      |
| House         | tower | art-deco | cape-cod      | modern      |

