.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, bike, subway, quad-bike
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, alhambra, aristoff, chaman
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, electronic, blues, funk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose, lily, dahlia
 1. the person driving the subway is the fan of metal##1
 2. the person driving the skateboard is the fan of electronic##1
 3. the baccarat-smoker is the fan of metal##1
 4. the person who growslily is the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the fan of blues is the chaman-smoker##1
 6. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 8. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 9. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Transport          | skateboard  | quad-bike | subway     | bike |
| Cigar           | aristoff  | chaman      | baccarat | alhambra    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | blues  | metal    | funk  |
| Flower           | lily   | dahlia       | orchid       | rose      |

