.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
House: colonial, cottage, farmhouse, townhouse
4 different games are played: scrabble, mah-jongg, bridge, billiard
There 4 different types of food: avocado, cucumber, cauliflower, zucchini
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, baccarat, montecristo, vegafina
 1. the person eating avocado is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the cottage house##1
 3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 4. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
 7. the person eating avocado is the montecristo-smoker##1
 8. the colonial house is on the far left##1
 9. the colonial house is on the left of the cottage house##1
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| House    | colonial | cottage     | farmhouse    | townhouse |
| Game       | scrabble | bridge    | billiard | mah-jongg |
| Food         | cucumber   | cauliflower  | zucchini        | avocado    |
| Cigar   | vegafina   | baccarat | bolivar    | montecristo |

