The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing, traveling, photography
There 4 different types of food: garlic, corn, watermelon, peas
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, chaman, montecristo, swisher
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person eating peas##1
2. the fan of r&b is the person eating watermelon##1
3. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
6. the person eating garlic is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is the aristoff-smoker##1
8. the montecristo-smoker is the fan of salsa##1
9. the swisher-smoker is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre      | r&b      | salsa         | ambient        | reggae      |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | board-games | traveling  | photography  |
| Food   | watermelon    | garlic     | corn | peas     |
| Cigar     | aristoff        | montecristo     | chaman     | swisher |

