.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-9::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, swisher, davidoff, pall-mall
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, mah-jongg, canasta
House: tower, wooden, art-deco, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, brazilian, egyptian
1. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
2. the canadian is on the right of the wooden house##1
3. the person playing whist is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the brazilian is on the right of the art-deco house##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the egyptian is the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the brazilian is the tower house##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left##1
9. the person playing canasta is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Cigar         | swisher | pall-mall | davidoff | baccarat     |
| Game   | mah-jongg   | canasta       | bridge       | whist  |
| House           | futuristic    | wooden    | art-deco       | tower       |
| Nationality     | argentine     | egyptian        | canadian   | brazilian |

