3. the futuristic house is on the far left##1
4. the gothic-revival house is the person playing scrabble##1
5. the modern house is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
8. the person playing monopoly is the modern house##1
9. the person eating lime is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| House      | futuristic     | modern           | wooden    | gothic-revival    |
| Game         | canasta  | monopoly | backgammon  | scrabble |
