6. the person playing go is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
7. the cottage house is on the left of the victorian house##1
8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Flower          | marigold | lily     | daffodil       | amaryllis |
